author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Exciting News: I'm taking Justin Hawkins Rides Again on tour across the UK ....again in January 2026. For anyone who enjoys my YouTube show on this here YouTube channel,  I can promise you more of the same,  but live and with an added sprinkle of chaos. 

Tickets go on sale on Friday 11 July  here: 
https://www.aegpresents.co.uk/event/justin-hawkins-rides-again/

Members of my Patreon will have early access to my presale from tomorrow. The link can be found here: 
http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

I hope to see you on the road!
title: Justin Hawkins Rides Again.....Again On Tour!
